<HEADLINE>
<P>
MARDI MARANS; PARAMOUNT EXECUTIVE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Mardi Marans, 41, executive vice president of Paramount and former vice 
president of Warner Bros. Born in Boston and educated at UC Berkeley, Miss 
Marans was a recognized spokeswoman for the entertainment industry as publicity 
chairwoman for the Motion Picture Assn. of America. On Wednesday in Los Angeles 
of a brain tumor. 
</P>
