CONFRONTATIONS; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- IRAQ; UNITED STATES -- 
ARMED FORCES -- SAUDI ARABIA; HUSSEIN, SADDAM; PUBLIC OPINION; QUALITY OF LIFE 
</P>
