CONFRONTATIONS; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- IRAQ; UNITED STATES -- 
ARMED FORCES -- PERSIAN GULF; KUWAIT -- EMBASSIES; AMERICANS -- KUWAIT; ESCAPES 
</P>
