<TEXT>
<P>
The Peggy Sue immortalized in song by rock 'n' roll pioneer Buddy Holly 
returned to Texas to judge a Buddy Holly look-alike contest. 
</P>
<P>
But Peggy Sue Rackham of Sacramento could not make up her mind Saturday. She 
chose co-winners, Sherrell Wilson and Richard Edwards, both of Slaton. 
</P>
